aming policies like SnakeCaseLower and KebabCaseLower, but I'm uncertain about the exact version that added PascalCase support.\n\nSince the user is asking about .NET 11 specifically, I'll just test it by creating a project and attempting to use `JsonNamingPolicy.PascalCase` to see if it's available on their system.\n\nWriting the test program...","outputTokens":1251,"requestId":"6C05:22A1A7:15D156:19B713:69FA8F6C"},"id":"18a65e90-f697-49ed-95be-4336a5337995","timestamp":"2026-05-06T00:46:57.979Z","parentId":"aca8e774-dcfd-4cff-9ddb-0b3f317bc3e6"}
